513
00:52:15.551 --> 00:52:17.252
through phone. Skype.

514
00:52:18.620 --> 00:52:19.988
- She must come visit.

515
00:52:20.756 --> 00:52:22.157
- Not so much.

516
00:52:22.157 --> 00:52:24.259
